data.description: BACK ON MARKET _ NO FAULT OF SELLER> Welcome to 11211 Foster Rd. Lot B – An Investment Opportunity with Lakeside Serenity! LAKE LIFE!!! This 2018 single-wide mobile home is not your average property; it's in impeccable shape and holds significant potential. Currently, it's a reliable source of rental income, and with its outstanding condition, it's poised to continue generating returns. The charm of this place extends beyond the mobile home itself – there's a delightful "she shed" or "man cave" guesthouse that adds a unique touch to the property and is also generating monthly income to the current owner! What truly sets this property apart is its income potential. Currently listed on VRBO, it's already a money-making machine with plenty of room for growth. With the right vision, you could maximize the returns and make this a lucrative investment. Beyond the structures, the property stretches all the way to the lakefront, offering the possibility of installing your own private dock around the beach area. Imagine having easy access to the serene waters right at your doorstep. Parking won't be an issue, as there's ample space for multiple vehicles. Privacy abounds on this lot, making it a perfect retreat from the hustle and bustle of everyday life. One of the property's most enchanting features is the sound of cascading waterfalls from the neighboring lot. Sit on your front deck or porch and let the soothing sounds of nature serenade you. To sweeten the deal, the owner is willing to consider a price break if you decide to purchase both Lot A and Lot B together, offering you even more opportunities for investment and enjoyment. Don't miss out on this unique chance to own a property that combines income potential, lakeside tranquility, and the allure of cascading waterfalls – all in one place! Video: https://sites.crossgaterealtymedia.com/media/download.asp?ECE6F402440A472BB12902A3C3513D3F
